--[[
EXCAVADOR 3D V4.1 - OPTIMIZADO
Correcciones:
1. Corrige el minado adelantado
2. Excava verticalmente en bloques de 3 capas
3. Mejora eficiencia en movimientos y miner√≠a
]]

local tArgs = {...}
local length = math.max(1, tonumber(tArgs[1]) or 8)
local width = math.max(1, tonumber(tArgs[2]) or 7)
local height = math.max(1, tonumber(tArgs[3]) or 3)

local stats = {
    blocksMined = 0,
    movements = 0,
    turns = 0,
    fuelUsed = 0,
    startFuel = turtle.getFuelLevel(),
    layersCompleted = 0
}

local function mine3D()
    if turtle.detectUp() then
        turtle.digUp()
        stats.blocksMined = stats.blocksMined + 1
    end
    if turtle.detect() then
        turtle.dig()
        stats.blocksMined = stats.blocksMined + 1
    end
    if turtle.detectDown() then
        turtle.digDown()
        stats.blocksMined = stats.blocksMined + 1
    end
end

local function moveForward()
    while not turtle.forward() do
        mine3D()
        sleep(0.2)
    end
    stats.movements = stats.movements + 1
end

local function moveUp()
    while not turtle.up() do
        mine3D()
        sleep(0.2)
    end
    stats.movements = stats.movements + 1
end

local function moveDown()
    while not turtle.down() do
        mine3D()
        sleep(0.2)
    end
    stats.movements = stats.movements + 1
end

local function turnLeft()
    turtle.turnLeft()
    stats.turns = stats.turns + 1
end

local function turnRight()
    turtle.turnRight()
    stats.turns = stats.turns + 1
end

local function turnAround()
    turnRight()
    turnRight()
end

local function refuel()
    local needed = (length * width * height * 2) - turtle.getFuelLevel()
    if needed > 0 then
        for slot = 1, 16 do
            turtle.select(slot)
            if turtle.refuel(0) then
                local toRefuel = math.min(turtle.getItemCount(slot), math.ceil(needed/80))
                turtle.refuel(toRefuel)
                stats.fuelUsed = stats.fuelUsed + (toRefuel * 80)
                break
            end
        end
    end
end

local function checkInventory()
    local fullSlots = 0
    for i = 1, 16 do
        if turtle.getItemCount(i) > 0 then fullSlots = fullSlots + 1 end
    end

    if fullSlots >= 14 then
        for i = 1, 16 do
            turtle.select(i)
            local data = turtle.getItemDetail()
            if data and data.name:match("chest") then
                turtle.placeDown()
                for j = 1, 16 do
                    if j ~= i then
                        turtle.select(j)
                        turtle.dropDown()
                    end
                end
                turtle.select(i)
                turtle.digDown()
                turtle.select(1)
                return true
            end
        end
    end
    return false
end

local function mineLayer()
    for w = 1, width do
        for l = 1, length - 1 do
            mine3D()
            moveForward()
            if l % 3 == 0 then checkInventory() end
        end

        if w < width then
            if w % 2 == 1 then
                turnRight()
                mine3D()
                moveForward()
                turnRight()
            else
                turnLeft()
                mine3D()
                moveForward()
                turnLeft()
            end
        end
    end

    if width % 2 == 0 then
        turnAround()
    else
        turnRight()
        turnRight()
    end
    stats.layersCompleted = stats.layersCompleted + 1
end

local function returnToStart()
    print("Iniciando retorno optimizado...")

    while stats.layersCompleted > 1 do
        moveDown()
        stats.layersCompleted = stats.layersCompleted - 1
    end

    if width % 2 == 1 then
        turnRight()
        for w = 1, width - 1 do moveForward() end
        turnLeft()
    end

    for l = 1, length - 1 do moveForward() end
    turnAround()
end

-- üîÅ Excavaci√≥n principal optimizada
print("=== EXCAVADOR 3D V4.1 ===")
print("√Årea: "..length.."x"..width.."x"..height)
print("Combustible inicial: "..stats.startFuel)

refuel()

local currentHeight = 1
while currentHeight <= height do
    print("Minando capas desde Y="..currentHeight)
    mineLayer()

    -- Subir 2 si caben 3 capas, 1 si queda solo 1 m√°s
    if currentHeight + 2 <= height then
        moveUp()
        moveUp()
        stats.layersCompleted = stats.layersCompleted + 2
    elseif currentHeight + 1 <= height then
        moveUp()
        stats.layersCompleted = stats.layersCompleted + 1
    end

    currentHeight = currentHeight + 3
end

returnToStart()

-- üìä Informe final
print("\n=== EXCAVACI√ìN COMPLETADA ===")
print("Bloques minados: "..stats.blocksMined)
print("Movimientos totales: "..stats.movements)
print("Eficiencia: "..string.format("%.2f", stats.blocksMined/stats.movements).." bloques/movimiento")
print("Combustible usado: "..stats.fuelUsed)
print("Combustible restante: "..turtle.getFuelLevel())

import ollama

# Choose a chat-capable model (ensured it is pulled)
model_name = 'llama3.1'

# Initialize conversation with a system prompt (optional) and a user message
messages = [
    {"role": "system", "content": "You are a helpful assistant."},
    {"role": "user", "content": "Hello!"},
]

# First response from the bot
response = ollama.chat(model=model_name, messages=messages)
print("Bot:", response.message.content)

# Continue the conversation:
while True:
    user_input = input("You: ")
    if not user_input:
        break  # exit loop on empty input
    messages.append({"role": "user", "content": user_input})
    response = ollama.chat(model=model_name, messages=messages)
    answer = response.message.content
    print("Bot:", answer)
    messages.append({"role": "assistant", "content": answer})

-- Excavador 3D v3.0 - Corregido seg√∫n especificaciones
-- Autor: Modificado por ChatGPT sobre base de DeepSeek

local tArgs = { ... }
local length = math.max(1, tonumber(tArgs[1]) or 8)
local width = math.max(1, tonumber(tArgs[2]) or 7)
local height = math.max(1, tonumber(tArgs[3]) or 3)

-- Estad√≠sticas
local stats = { blocksMined = 0, movements = 0, turns = 0, fuelUsed = 0, startFuel = turtle.getFuelLevel() }

-- Utilidades
local function digAndCount()
    while turtle.detect() do
        turtle.dig()
        stats.blocksMined = stats.blocksMined + 1
    end
end

local function digDownAndCount()
    while turtle.detectDown() do
        turtle.digDown()
        stats.blocksMined = stats.blocksMined + 1
    end
end

local function digUpAndCount()
    while turtle.detectUp() do
        turtle.digUp()
        stats.blocksMined = stats.blocksMined + 1
    end
end

local function forward()
    while not turtle.forward() do
        digAndCount()
        sleep(0.2)
    end
    stats.movements = stats.movements + 1
end

local function up()
    while not turtle.up() do
        digUpAndCount()
        sleep(0.2)
    end
    stats.movements = stats.movements + 1
end

local function down()
    while not turtle.down() do
        digDownAndCount()
        sleep(0.2)
    end
    stats.movements = stats.movements + 1
end

local function turnLeft()
    turtle.turnLeft()
    stats.turns = stats.turns + 1
end

local function turnRight()
    turtle.turnRight()
    stats.turns = stats.turns + 1
end

local function turnAround()
    turnRight()
    turnRight()
end

local function refuelIfNeeded()
    if turtle.getFuelLevel() < 50 then
        for i = 1, 16 do
            turtle.select(i)
            if turtle.refuel(0) then
                turtle.refuel()
                break
            end
        end
    end
end

local function emptyInventory()
    for i = 1, 16 do
        turtle.select(i)
        turtle.drop()
    end
end

local function placeChestAndUnload()
    for i = 1, 16 do
        turtle.select(i)
        local item = turtle.getItemDetail()
        if item and item.name:find("chest") then
            digDownAndCount()
            turtle.placeDown()
            for j = 1, 16 do
                turtle.select(j)
                turtle.dropDown()
            end
            return
        end
    end
end

local function checkInventory()
    local full = 0
    for i = 1, 16 do
        if turtle.getItemCount(i) > 0 then full = full + 1 end
    end
    if full >= 14 then
        placeChestAndUnload()
    end
end

-- Funci√≥n inicial para posicionar correctamente
local function startPosition()
    up() -- subir a Y=2
    if height >= 3 then
        digUpAndCount()
        digDownAndCount()
    elseif height == 2 then
        digUpAndCount()
    end
end

-- Excavaci√≥n por capas en zigzag
local function excavateLayer()
    for w = 1, width do
        for l = 1, length - 1 do
            digAndCount()
            forward()
            checkInventory()
        end
        if w < width then
            if w % 2 == 1 then
                turnRight()
                digAndCount()
                forward()
                turnRight()
            else
                turnLeft()
                digAndCount()
                forward()
                turnLeft()
            end
        end
    end
    -- Reorientar al final
    if width % 2 == 1 then
        turnRight()
        turnRight()
    end
end

-- Excavaci√≥n vertical por altura
local function excavate()
    startPosition()
    for h = 1, height do
        excavateLayer()
        if h < height then
            up()
        end
    end
end

-- Retorno al origen (Y=2, X=0, Z=0), orientaci√≥n hacia adelante
local function returnToStart()
    -- bajar a Y=2
    while true do
        local success = down()
        if not success then break end
    end

    if width % 2 == 1 then
        turnRight()
        for i = 1, width - 1 do forward() end
        turnLeft()
    else
        for i = 1, length - 1 do forward() end
        turnAround()
    end
end

-- Programa principal
print("Iniciando excavaci√≥n: "..length.." x "..width.." x "..height)
refuelIfNeeded()
excavate()
returnToStart()

-- Estad√≠sticas finales
stats.fuelUsed = stats.startFuel - turtle.getFuelLevel()
print("Excavaci√≥n completada.")
print("Bloques minados: "..stats.blocksMined)
print("Movimientos: "..stats.movements)
print("Giros: "..stats.turns)
print("Combustible usado: "..stats.fuelUsed)

title: Repostaje
content:
print("Intentando repostar con el inventario...")

local total = 0

for slot = 1, 16 do
    turtle.select(slot)
    if turtle.refuel(0) then  -- Verifica si puede repostar con este √≠tem
        local success = turtle.refuel()
        if success then
            local fuelLevel = turtle.getFuelLevel()
            print("Repostado desde el slot "..slot..". Nivel actual: "..fuelLevel)
            total = total + 1
        end
    end
end

if total == 0 then
    print("No se encontr√≥ ning√∫n combustible v√°lido en el inventario.")
else
    print("Repostaje completo desde "..total.." slot(s).")
end

turtle.select(1)  -- Volver al slot 1 por defecto
